'''''Boesman na Lena''''' ni ikinamico ngufi yakorewe muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika y'Epfo]] ikozwe na  Athol Fugard<ref>Boesman and Lena | work by Fugard | Britannica</ref>,  Swartkops mudflats hamwe na  Port Elizabeth mur Cape town y'iburasirazuba, <ref>[http://www.encyclopedia.com/arts/educational-magazines/boesman-lena "Boesman & Lena"], Encyclopedia.com.</ref> yerekana ingaruka ya apartheid ku bantu bakeya,  hagaragaramo "umugabo n'umugore bagenda bava mu mujyi umwe bajya mu wundi<ref>Boesman and Lena (1974) | Radio Times <nowiki>https://www.radiotimes.com</nowiki> › movie-guide › boesman-...</ref>.

== Amavu n'amavuko ==
Mubisanzwe hamwe nibindi bikorwa byinshi bya Fugard, ikinamico yibanda ku bantu batari abazungu kandi ikubiyemo ibintu byo kwigaragambya<ref>DLT Boesman and Lena - Longfield Hall <nowiki>https://longfieldhall.org.uk</nowiki> › dark-and-light-theatre-boe...</ref>. ''Boesman na Lena'' batewe inkunga n'ibyabaye mu 1965 igihe Fugard yari atwaye mu umuhanda wo mu cyaro muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika]] y'Epfo<ref>Film Notes - Boesman and Lena - University at Albany <nowiki>https://www.albany.edu</nowiki> › writers-inst › webpages4 › fil...</ref>. Yabonye umukecuru ugenda mu muhanda izuba ryamwishe, ku bilometero uvuye aho agana, maze amuha lift. Yaratsinzwe ararira ashimira<ref>Three Port Elizabeth plays : The blood knot : Hello and goodbye <nowiki>https://www.worldcat.org</nowiki> › title › oclc</ref>. Yamubwiye ko umugabo we yari amaze gupfa kandi ko yari yagiye mu rindi sambu. iyo Fugard adahagarara, yari kurara kumuhanda<ref>Boesman & Lena | Encyclopedia.com</ref>.  (Byari akamenyero muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika y'Epfo ivangura rishingiye]] ku gitsina abahinzi birukana imiryango y'abakozi igihe umukozi yapfaga. )<ref>Lifetime Tony Award for Athol Fugard | Brand South Africa <nowiki>https://www.brandsouthafrica.com</nowiki> › ... › Arts and Culture</ref> Icyatangaje Fugard nuko umugore yari afite ububabare  ariko akaba ataratsinzwe. Ibi byamuteye kwandika ikinamico<ref>Boesman and Lena Analysis - eNotes.com <nowiki>https://www.enotes.com</nowiki> › topics › boesman › in-depth</ref>.
